Package: Rdataflow
Type: Package
Title: Reverse-Engineer and Visualize Data Flow in R Scripts
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Jasper", "Cain",
      email = "jcainsecondemail@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Given an R object and the script that produced it, Rdataflow
    traces back through the assignments and transformations that were applied
    to the source data to create the object, and renders the resulting lineage
    as a flow diagram.
